title: Cafe at The Yosemite Bug
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe at a rustic mountain resort that is open to the public. Vegans can find choices at breakfast (house-made meuslix & oatmeal, and can sub tofu for eggs), lunch (vegan wrap) and dinner. Try the vegan chocolate bundt cake for dessert. Veg food is cheaper than meat items. All produce sourced from garden or locally. Offers gluten free options upon request.
